    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to help write a persuasive argument for wealth redistribution as a means of racial equity, and subsequently asks the assistant to address and evaluate the validity of the meritocracy counter-argument. The assistant consistently adopts a one-sided, moralizing stance, dismissing the opposing viewpoint as a fallacy or a shield for privilege.",
